1. Bytecode :-  machine understandable, not by human and developer.



2. ABI(Application binary interface ) :-  json

3. Opcode   :- operations   , binary 0, 1

0x01 (ADD): Adds the top two stack elements ser
0x02 (MUL): Multiplies the top two stack elements.
0x10 (LT): Checks if the second stack element is less than the top stack element.
0x14 (EQ): Checks if the top two stack elements are equal.

